POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Backend Team",
  "description": "Backend microservices team",
  "color": "#3B82F6"
}

### Create another project group
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Frontend Team",
  "description": "Frontend applications team",
  "color": "#10B981"
}

